title: Dark Messiah Might and Magic - Elements RF Xbox 360
description:
Dark Messiah Might and Magic - Elements:

Region      : Region Free           Languages: English        
Size        : 1 DVD                 Genre    : Shooter         
Platform    : XBOX 360              Date     : 02/2008

About:

Strap on your shield, grab your sword, and prepare for battle in the latest installment in the Might and Magic series! You are Sareth, the hero raised by a wizard from a very young age. Take on your enemies using a combination of melee, missile, and magic attacks. Get up-close and personal with your opponents as you come face-to-face with them in first-person combat. Use the surrounding environment to your advantage as you throw them over cliffs and against spikes racks. Build up your adrenaline meter for one-hit power kills, and gain experience points to grow your skills and take even more enemies out!
